<table width="600">
	<tr>
		<td>
			<h1 align="center">CANDID</h1>
			<hr>			
		
			<p><b>Developed by:</b><br>Los Alamos National Laboratory, USA </p>
			
			<p>
			<b>Features:</b><br> 
			Color, texture, and shape features are extracted from the image on pixel basis.  Feature vectors of all pixels forms a point set in higher-dimension space, which defines the signature of the image.
			</p>
			
			<p>
			<b>Matching:</b><br>
			Normalized Euclidean distances between two signatures or inner product of the two signature
			</p>
			
			<p>
			<b>Querying:</b><br>
			User submits a query image.
			<i><br>
			&nbsp;</i></p>
			
		</td>
	</tr>
</table>
